name: Still Life Collab #001
description: My child and I have decided to start a still life collab series. This is the first piece.  They had recently heard of a 'vintage lifehack' involving the use of potatoes as a way to keep cut flowers fresh.  Here is the result of our work.  It is a metaphor of the way we carry on even when we are not OK. The refrigerator as a backdrop invokes American domesticity, while the underwater lighting lends itself to the overall emotion of the piece.
